    codex.md
    docs/REGRESSION_CHECKS.md
    docs/UAV_CONTROL_API.md
    docs/VISUALIZATION_GUIDE.md
    TOOLS_AND_SCRIPTS_GUIDE.md
    ```

12. Final reports must include:

    ```text
    changed files
    commands run
    test result
    known risks
    output paths, when logs or visualizations were generated
    ```

